        <abstract> 
<p>The review of EBT’s book ["Primitive Man: Tylor and Lubbock"] in the <hi rend="italic">Quarterly Review</hi> [137: 40–77] last year contained a false and malicious attack on CD’s son George. CD knows it was written by St George Mivart. CD wishes to take every opportunity to say how false a man he considers him to be.</p> 
        </abstract>
